name: Rocket-Belt
description:
Welcome to Rocket-Belt!

You have broken into a top-secret laboratory to steal some stuff. 

But what you find is not what you expected.

The badguys have managed to create a infinite room full of traps, spikewheels, and more. 

You, determined not to give up, try to survive as long as possible. 

What? What's Jetpack Joyride?

Eh whatever.

Have a great day!!
